Class IntegerTrial

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.T05.krowdtrialz.model.trial.Trial
      • com.T05.krowdtrialz.model.trial.IntegerTrial

  • public class IntegerTrial
extends Trial
    IntegerTrials hold a single value which is the output of the trial. The integer value could represent something like "number of laps completed in 10 min." for instance.
